/*Day 3 â€“ Health & Wellness Voice Companion (Murf AI Voice Agent Challenge)

This update introduces a fully functional Health & Wellness Voice Companion designed to perform structured daily check-ins, provide actionable wellness suggestions, and persist user data across sessions.

Core Features

Real-time voice-to-text transcription integrated into the frontend.

Persistent wellness logging using a JSON-based storage model.

Context-aware dialogue, enabling the agent to reference previous check-ins.

Automatic transcript clearing on the frontend while preserving backend history.

Technical Highlights

Implemented @function_tool decorators as instance methods for seamless integration with the LLM.

Added read/write utilities for wellness_log.json with timestamped entries.

Designed a grounded, non-clinical system prompt focusing on practical wellness guidance.

Established stable communication between frontend and backend through the LiveKit Agent Framework.

Integrated Murf Falcon TTS for fast, natural-sounding responses.

What the Agent Can Do

Conduct structured daily health/wellness check-ins.

Suggest simple, actionable steps (e.g., taking a walk, breaking goals into small tasks).

Persist each session to the JSON log for future reference.

Provide a consistent conversational experience across days.

Demo

The included video shows the complete workflow, including real-time updates to wellness_log.json as the conversation progresses.


  
